These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, mirinda, cola, iced-tea
The people have 5 different jobs:  police-officer, scientist, librarian, musician, engineer
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, pop, electronic, rock, dubstep
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, malaysian, mexican, australian, pakistani
 1. the mexican is on the left or right of the engineer##3
 2. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan of country is on the left of the malaysian##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the engineer is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the pakistani is in an even position##4
 9. the italian is on the left or right of the musician##3
10. the fan of electronic is the librarian##1
11. the fan of pop is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the malaysian##1
14. the pakistani is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
15. the fan of rock is the person drinking cola##1
16. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | 7up   | cola     | iced-tea      | juice      |
| Job           | librarian | engineer | police-officer    | musician | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | electronic       | country         | rock      | pop      | dubstep    |
| Nationality   | mexican    | australian         | malaysian | pakistani  | italian   |

