.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, sudoku, dancing, hiking, magic-tricks
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, rock, country, pop, r&b
5 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, frog, mouse, hamster
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, tram, car, van, jet-ski
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of r&b##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 6. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person driving the ship##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
11. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
13. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
14. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | hiking | sudoku | dancing   | writing | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | country      | rock   | r&b    | dubstep        | pop        |
| Pet           | mouse         | hamster  | lizard  | ferret   | frog      |
| Transport     | ship        | van  | car | jet-ski | tram         |

