.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, tea, water, mirinda
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, disaster, epic, zombie
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, golf, sailing, snowboarding, rugby
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, ship, bus, snowmobile, subway
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the bus##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is golf##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is between the person driving the ship and the person watching adventure movies##2
13. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
14. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
16. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
| Beverage      | mirinda       | almond-milk   | soy-milk    | water     | tea |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | satire   | disaster   | epic | zombie       |
| Sport         | rugby | golf | water-polo | snowboarding     | sailing        |
| Transport     | snowmobile       | car     | ship  | bus   | subway         |

