.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-4::.
There 5 different types of food: kiwi, radish, zucchini, lemon, pineapple
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, martial-arts, comedy, family
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, indie, blues, funk, country
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, skateboard, tram, subway, car
 1. the person driving the skateboard is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person driving the boat##2
 2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 3. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 4. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
 5. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 6. the person driving the car is the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 9. the person eating pineapple is the fan of country##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
14. the person eating kiwi is the person eating kiwi##1
15. the person driving the subway is the person watching family movies##1
16. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
17. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi   | lemon   | radish | zucchini       | pineapple       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | family     | martial-arts   | adventure     | comedy    |
