 3. the american is on the far left##1
 4. the dutch is on the left of the german##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 8. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the mexican##3
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
11. the person driving the boat is the american##1
12. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is climbing##1
14. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the american##1
16. the person drinking almond-milk is the australian##1

