The people prefer 5 different types of sport: snowboarding, climbing, surfing, swimming, cycling
 1. the person eating pumpkin is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
 4. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's sport is cycling and the owner of the lizard##2
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is swimming and the owner of the frog##2
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the person eating lemon is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the person eating pineapple is in the middle##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
12. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
14. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
15. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
16. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
