 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 5. the brazilian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 8. the owner of the lizard is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person eating apricot##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the japanese##1
10. the canadian is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
11. the canadian is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
13. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
14. the person eating apricot is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Food          | apricot      | garlic       | corn | grapefruit | cauliflower |
| Nationality   | indonesian       | french    | brazilian  | japanese  | canadian |
| Pet           | ferret         | lizard | horse      | goldfish     | cat    |
| Sport         | rugby | ice-hockey   | swimming   | parkour  | biathlon |

